              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Bare samples considered: The samples, located at",
                "opposite ends of an aluminum capsule, each consisted",
                "of about 25 mg U3O8 spread out over an area of about",
                "1.1 cm in a small aluminum can. The capsule was",
                "irradiated close enough to the central plane of the",
                "reactor for the effects of the vertical flux gradient",
                "to be negligible."
              ]
